headline: Prediction: Lyft Stock Could Double in the Next 3 Years
summary: Lyft's business has improved significantly over the last three years.  The ride-share company is expanding into Europe with its recently announced acquisition of FreeNow.  It continues to add new features like Lyft Silver.
